<p>I would like to thank my colleagues Oliver Bilodeau, Sebastian Bortnik, Bruce Burrell and David Harley for their feedback while researching this topic.</p>
<p>Do you use Linux on the desktop and, if so, have you ever come across malware, either for it or another operating system?  Do you also run anti-malware software on your Linux desktops?  Why or why not?  Let us know below!</p>
<p><strong>Aryeh Goretsky, MVP, ZCSE<br />
